products.name: IPhone 15
products.Description: The innovative new design features back glass that has color infused throughout the material. A custom dual ion-exchange process for the glass, and an aerospace-grade aluminum enclosure, help make iPhone 15 incredibly durable. Dependably durable.

products.name: Ps5
products.Description: Powered by an eight-core AMD Zen 2 CPU and custom AMD Radeon GPU, the PS5 is offered in two models: with and without a 4K Blu-ray drive. Supporting a 120Hz video refresh, the PS5 is considerably more powerful than the PS4 and PS4 Pro.
